Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I select C0 to Os coccygis vertebras on the localizer of Page 01
And	I go to Page 06 of Spine MRI

When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then 'Finding' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Fracture' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And Localizer is enabled

When I click on the Localizer
Then the localizer canvas opens
And C0 to Os coccygis vertebras are active and enabled

When I click on any vertebra from C3 to L5
And I close the localizer canvas
Then 'A0 Classification' radio button is enabled
And 'Genant Classification' radio button is enabled
And 'Fracture, not further defined' radio button is enabled

When I select 'A0 Classification' radio button
Then 'A: Compression injury' radio button is enabled
And 'B: Tension band injury' radio button is enabled
And 'C: Displacement/translational injury' radio button is enabled

When I select 'A: Compression injury' radio button
Then 'A0: Minor nonstructural fracture' radio button is enabled
And 'A1: Wedge fracture [wedge compression]' radio button is enabled
And 'A2: Cleavage fracture' radio button is enabled
And 'A3 : Burst fracture, incomplete (fracture of upper or lower endplate)' radio button is enabled
And 'A4 : Burst fracture, complete (fracture of upper or lower endplate)' radio button is enabled

When I select 'B: Tension band injury' radio button..
Then 'B1: Transossare Fission fracture (chance fracture)' radio button is enabled
And 'B2: Tear of the posterior tension band and incomplete burst fracture' radio button is enabled
And 'B3: Destruction of the intervertebral disc and tear of the anterior tension band' radio button is enabled


When I select 'Genant Classification' radio button
Then 'Mild fracture, grade 1' radio button is enabled
And 'Moderate fracture, grade 2' radio button is enabled
And 'Severe fracture, grade 3' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Mild fracture, grade 1' radio button
Then 'Wedge fracture' radio button is enabled
And 'Biconcave fracture' radio button is enabled
And 'Crush fracture' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Moderate fracture, grade 2' radio button
Then 'Wedge fracture' radio button is enabled
And 'Biconcave fracture' radio button is enabled
And 'Crush fracture' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Severe fracture, grade 3' radio button
Then 'Wedge fracture' radio button is enabled
And 'Biconcave fracture' radio button is enabled
And 'Crush fracture' radio button is enabled


When I select 'Fracture, not further defined' radio button
Then 'Appearance of an older fracture, consolidated' radio button is enabled
And 'Suspicion of' radio button is enabled
And 'Height loss, standard variant' radio button is enabled
And 'Scheuermann's disease' radio button is enabled
And 'Vertebra Remodelling (for osteochondrosis)' radio button is enabled
And 'Dysplasia' radio button is enabled
And 'Bone marrow edema' radio button is enabled

When I select 'Height loss, standard variant' radio button
Then 'Secondary' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Scheuermann's disease' radio button
Then 'Secondary' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Vertebra Remodelling (for osteochondrosis)' radio button
Then 'Secondary' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Dysplasia' radio button
Then 'Schmorl node' checkbox is enabled
And 'Secondary' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Bone marrow edema' radio button
Then 'Secondary' checkbox is enabled








When I select 'Axis arc' radio button
Then 'Effendi/Levine Type 1' radio button is enabled
And 'Effendi/Levine Type 2' radio button is enabled
And 'Effendi/Levine Type 2a' radio button is enabled
And 'Effendi/Levine Type 3' radio button is enabled

When I select 'C2 Fracture, not further specified' radio button
Then 'Suspicion of' radio button is enabled
And 'Appearance of an older fracture, consolidated' radio button is enabled
And 'Stability' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Stability' checkbox
Then 'Stable' radio button is enabled
And 'Unstable' radio button is enabled


When I select 'C1-C2' radio button
Then 'Subluxation with rotation' radio button is enabled
And 'Displacement' radio button is enabled
